devdoc.details: A lottery system where users can buy tickets and a winner is randomly selected

buyTicket(uint256).details: Buy a ticket for a specified lottery

params.lotteryId: ID of the lottery to buy a ticket for

claimPrize(uint256,uint256).details: Claim the prize for a winning ticket

createLottery(uint256).details: Create a new lottery with specified ticket price

params.ticketPrice: Price per lottery ticket in wei

getLotteryInfo(uint256).details: Get information about a specific lottery

params.lotteryId: ID of the lottery to get information for

getTicketInfo(uint256,uint256).details: Get information about a specific ticket

pickWinner(uint256).details: Pick a winner for the lottery

params.lotteryId: ID of the lottery to pick a winner for
